data.title: 7 Locker Service. Pickup your packages anytime at The UPS Store 104 E 600 S, Heber City, UT
data.meta_description: The UPS Store 24/7 locker service lets you pickup your deliveries anytime. Safe, secure & ready when you are. Get started today.
data.text:
To access this service, first contact The UPS Store, or visit us at 104 E 600 S to register to use the 24/7 Lockers.

Then have your packages registered to be delivered to our location. Weâ€™ll send you a package alert and access code when your item arrives. To retrieve your package, simply enter the access code at the locker screen and grab your item anytime day or night!
